"v.同意，赞成 【英】 v. 同意，赞成(to express acceptance; concur, consent ) 【考】 反义词：buck(反对) 【记】 as+sent(感觉) →感觉一致→同意 【同】 同根词：dissent(反 对); resent(怨恨) 【例】 John refused to assent to the proposal. v. (与to连用)同意(某建议) = concur = consent 【例】I assented to your view 我同意你的看法. 【记】as一个, sent感觉－大家一个感觉－同意 【参】dissent(v 反对); resent(v 愤恨, 怨恨) 【反】buck(vt 顽强抵抗, 强烈反对) 【记】as 肯定 + sent 感觉→肯定你的感觉→肯定，consent 同意 【相关】absent (ab + present) 缺席，assent consent (同感) 同意，dissent (不同感) 不同意，(同感) 同意，present 现在，礼物，resent (反感)憎恨 assent (v.)  c.1300, from Old French assentir ""agree; get used to"" (12c.), from Latin assentare ""to agree with,"" frequentative of assentire, from ad- ""to"" (see ad-) + sentire ""to feel, think"" (see sense (n.)). Related: Assented; assenting. assent (n.)  early 14c., ""consent, approval,"" from Old French assent, a back-formation from assentir (see assent (v.))."
